extendedInfo.description: This is a mobile app for my new forum startup. Its a forum to help other with their android app development and publishing. Specifically aimed at people using Google app inventor.This is one of the first apps that i have made from the actual android sdk, so this is a bit new for me. Ive done java before so it wasn't that bad, but i've grown accustom to app inventor and its level of difficulty compared to this. Anyway, the point is, this will be a work in progress app. Im gonna do my best to update it and maybe integrate it better with the forums.
